{"tw": {"3172290": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Milfy Way: Space Orgasm 🪐🔞", "steam_appid": 3172290, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一名逃犯，也是罪犯，因走私過度刺激的情趣玩具而被定罪。在一場監獄暴動中，你成功逃脫，並偶然發現了一艘老舊又生鏽的太空船。壞消息？它在第一次超空間跳躍後就故障了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172290/extras/2292b59b2ee4f044545fb096f81c8609.poster.avif?t=1759345789\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172290/extras/2292b59b2ee4f044545fb096f81c8609.webm?t=1759345789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172290/extras/2292b59b2ee4f044545fb096f81c8609.mp4?t=1759345789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >現在你必須親自動手修復飛船，否則別想抵達目的地。而目的地是哪？在你被捕之前，你偷偷把一批……不，是超級龐大的違禁貨藏在一個遙遠的星球上。如果你能找到它，你就能變得比以往任何時候都更富有！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但這不僅僅是一段逃亡故事——這是一場充滿火辣邂逅、刺激情節與誘惑機會的成人冒險旅程。你將在宇宙中收集資源、打造工具（或偷窺裝置）、與黑市商人交易、處理船艙日常雜事，並參與瘋狂任務！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172290/extras/cd121e3ec139fb784aa10d457dbd29a8.poster.avif?t=1759345789\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172290/extras/cd121e3ec139fb784aa10d457dbd29a8.webm?t=1759345789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172290/extras/cd121e3ec139fb784aa10d457dbd29a8.mp4?t=1759345789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中，你將遇見許多性感又有魅力的女主角——她們各有秘密與慾望，願意加入你的太空船隊。你將逐步認識她們的思想……和身體。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172290/extras/62ca0c48145867d8f88027edff8b1de2.poster.avif?t=1759345789\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172290/extras/62ca0c48145867d8f88027edff8b1de2.webm?t=1759345789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172290/extras/62ca0c48145867d8f88027edff8b1de2.mp4?t=1759345789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >登上你的太空船，組成你的船員團隊，探索浩瀚宇宙，尋回那批隱藏的走私寶藏，成為自由又富有、並被熱辣神秘女伴環繞的宇宙傳奇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>遊戲特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大膽成人內容 —— 發展關係並解鎖 18+ 互動場景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >強烈視覺風格 —— 高質感 2D 畫面與動畫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豐富玩法 —— 採集資源、製作、偷窺、隨機事件與火辣任務。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多樣角色 —— 每位角色皆性感誘人，有著獨特背景與個性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性感復古未來風格 —— 探索誘惑與神秘交織的銀河宇宙。</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一名逃犯，也是罪犯，因走私過度刺激的情趣玩具而被定罪。在一場監獄暴動中，你成功逃脫，並偶然發現了一艘老舊又生鏽的太空船。壞消息？它在第一次超空間跳躍後就故障了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172290/extras/2292b59b2ee4f044545fb096f81c8609.poster.avif?t=1759345789\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172290/extras/2292b59b2ee4f044545fb096f81c8609.webm?t=1759345789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172290/extras/2292b59b2ee4f044545fb096f81c8609.mp4?t=1759345789\" type=\"video/mp4\